1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Kitten Economics Episode 2: Supply and Demand.

2
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Welcome back. Today we learn one core economics idea with kittens.

3
00:00:45,000 --> 00:01:15,000
On Cat Street, rainbow feather toys suddenly become popular.

4
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:45,000
Many kittens want them, but only a few are available. Prices rise because demand is high and supply is low.

5
00:01:45,000 --> 00:02:10,000
Later, two more toy shops open and supply increases. Prices soften.

6
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:35,000
Recap: Supply and Demand. Use this rule in real decisions. Comment: More Kitten Economics.
